{"tid":519551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貧困公屋戶涉隱瞞1200萬資產重判罰款2萬4","createTime":"2018-01-04T12:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T21:02:32.000Z","uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"49a268ae6a3b1feb660d1f2bcee66b88355190e6","tid":519551,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"一名公屋住戶去年5月填寫資產申報表時，隱瞞擁有或管有市值1,170萬元房產，被法庭裁定虛假陳述罪成，判罰2.4萬元及監禁2個月，緩刑24個月。<br />\n房屋署發言人指，該名公屋住戶2017年5月向房署遞交一份資產申報表，而沒有申報擁有或管有任何房產。其後房署調查發現該公屋住戶刻意隱瞞擁有或管有房產，市值評估為1,170萬元。最終該名公屋住戶因違反《房屋條例》第26（1）（a）條，被控明知而作出虛假陳述。案件今日於屯門裁判法院進行聆訊，主審裁判官考慮到案情嚴重，判處罰款2.4萬元及監禁2個月，緩刑24個月。"},{"pid":"7182bbdbcb8c790d553d2fca3a384c6a290a6eb2","tid":519551,"uid":64355,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"真係好重判"},{"pid":"c18390655c297c2b2ddefc2b9226082ce87b587b","tid":519551,"uid":88723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"2萬4 2個月<br />\n值博率好高"},{"pid":"9fc100197e8687020f1a6386bc300685294142ba","tid":519551,"uid":69930,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"個人認為判刑過重"},{"pid":"51d02b53c33f2b99db190a4b0e1a85aa9e87e651","tid":519551,"uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c18390655c297c2b2ddefc2b9226082ce87b587b","tid":519551,"uid":88723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"2萬4 2個月<br />\n值博率好高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"跟本唔洗坐監"},{"pid":"241b3887502334bd3786fb237e2cfb7046728578","tid":519551,"uid":10929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"有無踢佢走"},{"pid":"ff5946bdb7312ae942b3a9a71000f4633d075e8f","tid":519551,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d02b53c33f2b99db190a4b0e1a85aa9e87e651","tid":519551,"uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c18390655c297c2b2ddefc2b9226082ce87b587b","tid":519551